To Die For;;1995;;R;;Comedy,Crime,Drama;;6.8;;Gus Van Sant;;Nicole Kidman,Matt Dillon,Joaquin Phoenix,Casey Affleck,Illeana Douglas,Alison Folland,Dan Hedaya,Wayne Knight,Kurtwood Smith,Holland Taylor,Susan Traylor,Maria Tucci,Tim Hopper,Michael Rispoli,Buck Henry,Gerry Quigley,Tom Forrester,Alan Edward Lewis;;Suzanne Stone (Kidman) knows exactly what she wants. She wants to be a television newscaster and she is willing to do anything to get what she wants. What she lacks in intelligence, she makes up for in cold determination and diabolical wiles. As she pursues her goal with relentless focus, she is forced to destroy anything and anyone that may stand in her way, regardless of the ultimate cost or means necessary.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0114681/